data.description: Nestled within the secure confines of a meticulously maintained gated senior community, this inviting single-family home offers a serene and active lifestyle for those seeking comfort and convenience in their golden years. With a host of desirable features both inside and out, this property provides a welcoming retreat to call home.  As you approach, you'll immediately notice the convenience of a 1-car garage and a carport, ensuring ample parking options for you and your guests. The patio provides an ideal spot for outdoor relaxation and gardening, while the large back yard beckons with possibilities for outdoor activities.  Step inside to discover a wealth of interior amenities. Gleaming wood flooring flows seamlessly throughout the living areas, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen is a chef's delight, boasting upgraded counters and stainless steel appliances that elevate both form and function. The adjacent breakfast nook is the perfect place to start your day with a cup of coffee.  The home is equipped with air conditioning to keep you comfortable year-round. Washer and dryer hookups are conveniently located for added laundry convenience. Vaulted ceilings throughout the home lend an airy and spacious feel, enhanced by strategically placed ceiling fans and skylights that infuse natural light into living spaces.  The guard- gated senior community offers an array of amenities to enhance your retirement lifestyle. On-site HOA management ensures a well-maintained and secure environment. Stay active and social with access to tennis and pickleball courts, providing opportunities for friendly competition and exercise. Golf enthusiasts will appreciate the nearby golf facilities, while the swimming pool is perfect for a leisurely dip or aqua aerobics.  The heart of the community is the spacious center, where you can engage in various clubs, dine with friends, or get lost in a good book at the library. This hub fosters a sense of camaraderie and connection among residents.  Conveniently situated within the gated senior community, this home offers both tranquility and easy access to nearby amenities, making it an ideal place to enjoy your retirement years to the fullest.  Don't miss your chance to own this delightful single-family home in a thriving senior community. Embrace the next chapter of your life in comfort and style. Schedule a viewing today to experience the welcoming ambiance and countless features this property has to offer.
